snippet.title: Meditation for Beginners | Day 1 of the 21 Day Meditation Challenge with Gurudev
snippet.description:
Meditation for Beginners | Day 1 of the 21 Day Meditation Challenge with Gurudev

In this short meditation, Gurudev guides you through the first few steps of turning within yourself, moving from the gross to the subtle, as you begin your practice.

For the next 21 days, make a commitment to meditate every day at 7:30 PM IST as Gurudev guides you through an amazing set of meditations.

To get notified daily join our WhatsApp group - http://www.aoliv.in/joinmeditation

Maximize happiness, health & immunity. Cut down stress, anxiety, and depression! Learn the powerful breathing technique Sudarshan Kriya, along with Pranayama, Yoga, Meditation and Practical Tips for everyday living in the online Meditation and Breath workshop (The Art of Living Happiness Program).

 Register now üëâüèΩ https://aolf.in/ytonlinehp

#21DayMeditationChallenge

About Gurudev Sri Sri Ravi Shankar

Gurudev Sri Sri Ravi Shankar is a world-renowned humanitarian, spiritual leader, and an ambassador of peace and human values. Through his life and work, Gurudev has inspired millions around the world with a vision of a stress-free and violence-free world.
Gurudev founded The Art of Living, a non-profit organization that is engaged in stress-management and service initiatives. The programs designed by Gurudev empower people with techniques and tools to live a deeper and blissful life.

#Gurudev #SriSriRaviShankar

snippet.title: BEFIKAR | Tanzeel Khan ft. Aashna Hegde
snippet.description:
GIVING YOU GUYS A PART OF OUR HEARTS WITH [ B E F I K A R ] üë´‚ô•Ô∏è

This song depicts young love, love that has no bounds! A song that‚Äôll make you feel all the emotions, that‚Äôll make you dance your heart away! So go enjoy this song with your loved ones, tell them you love them and always remember to love without any fikar, love Befikar!

#Befikar #TanzeelKhan #AashnaHegde

______________________________________
Audio
Artists : Tanzeel Khan & Aashna Hegde
Lyrics & Composition : Tanzeel Khan
Music : Akarsh Shetty

______________________________________

Amazon: https://music.amazon.in/albums/B08GNSP6BN

Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/album/33KloUY2J8WBQI5BisMJ8E

Gaana: https://gaana.com/song/befikar-5

Apple Music: https://music.apple.com/in/album/befikar-feat-aashna-hegde-single/1529243739

JioSaavn: https://www.jiosaavn.com/song/befikar/EwZGQzwCZVQ

Wynk: https://wynk.in/music/album/befikar/bl_3616408422176

YouTube Music: https://music.youtube.com/watch?v=01otGN_Qo1M&feature=share

Resso: https://m.resso.app/ZSPRdqp4/

____________________________________
Lyrics:

[Tanzeel]
Mera dil Meri jaaan
Mujhse na chupa
Chahat karde bayaaan
Mere dil ka kya? 

Dil mein hai baatein meri jo basi voh
Keh na saka mein tumse kabhi jo
Dena hai dil ab bas yeh tum hi ko
Chahat meri ab se tum hi ho

Kaise bhula du saari voh baatein
Khush bhi hu toh tere sahaare
Soye na ab hum kitni hi raatein
Paya hai tujko ab yeh jahan mein

Khwaabon mein tujhse milta raha
chah ke mein na keh yeh saka
Ki Tere bina kya wajood mera
hona nahi kabhi tujhse juda

(Hook) (X2)
Befikar hogaya 
mai kidhar kho gaya
Ishq ki raah me            
ab tu milgaya 

[Aashna]
Mera dil meri jaaan
Mujhsee na chupaaa
Chahat karde bayaan
Mere dil ka kya? 

Jaanu mein sab kuch ,jo tu chupaye 
Mere alava sabko bataye
Pyaar se haq mujhpe jo jataye 
Na jaane kyu itna tu sataye

Meri ye dhadkane be-sabar hai
Shayad tujhko bhi na khabar hai
Mere liye tu kitna alag hai
Teri chahat ki bhi samjh hai


Khwaabon mein tujhse milti rahi
Chah ke bhi kuch keh na saki , 
Jo Aaj bhi mein tujhme hi basi
Jaana na ab tu door kahi 

(Hook) x2
Befikar ho gaya 
Mai kidhar kho gaya
Ishq ki raah me               
Ab tu mil gaya

snippet.title: EMIWAY - THANKS TO GOD (Prod. by Pendo46) (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Lyrics given below

Artist & Lyrics - Emiway Bantai 

Music - Pendo46
https://www.youtube.com/user/Rillataan

Mix/Master - Emiway

Visuals by - Happy

Edited by -  Happy and Emiway

Production - Bantai studio 

Producer- Emiway Bantai

Emiway Management MAIL ID 
imailemiway@gmail.com

Social connect
Instagram - Emiway_Bantai
Facebook - Emiway37
Twitter - emiwaytweets

(Lyrics)
Ab mei accha karra tha
Abba ka kam hora tha thap par woh nai har manenge
Woh badalke rhenge kismat
Filal jo waqt tha woh kaagi saqt tha paisa usane se pehle deraha hu sadqah.Mujhe rehna hai strong Dhyan rakhna hai sabka pata bhi nai chala achanak se kaise tapka pareshani,chod gaya nishani yeah.Aj gana nai sunane aya hu kahani mei.

Subha ka waqt tha
Abba ke sar mei dard tha
Raat ko sone se pehle unke dil mei dar tha
Mummy ka call aya subhe boli woh jaldi se ghar aa
Mei bhagke jake dekha
Abba ka halat bigadta ja rha tha
andhar ka dard aj chehre pe dikha
Raha tha
Kha par leke jau kuch nhi smjh aa rha tha
Aese tese karke le gaya unko aspatal
Ek nai do nai teen nai char
Dekha nai tha unka aisa haal
Leke gaya unhe ambulance mei
Baithke
Pehchan nai rhe the abba
Mujhe dekhke
Mei dekhta hi rehgaya
Kafi din se roya nai tha lekin usdin behgaya
Malik pe tab bhi bharosa tha mei unse kehgaya
Man hi man mei
Mere abba ko lota do
Unke sapne ko pura karne ko firse ek mauka do
Theekh kaise karu mei unhe
rasta koi
Batado
Abba ko bachalo

Aisa lagra tha
Abba yad dash kho diye
Icu mei dekheke unhe ammi
Bhi roo diye
Par har nahi mane hum
Pata tha woh
Lotenge
Bure khayalat are the
Lekin hum
Rokenge
Chokenge jab dekhenge
Bhagwan ka karishma
Mei tut rha tha
Mujhe lagne laga sadma
Par anu ballu bhai Sumit minta
Shabana didi sab sath the
Family walo ne dia sath
Bole khuda sath hai

Sath hai khuda mere sath hai
Zindagi hai hi aisi cheez din
Kabhi raat hai (x3)
Sath hai sath hai khuda sabke
sath hai zindagi hai aisi cheez
Din kabhi raat hai kya

Alhumdulillah
All praises to allah
Almighty god is great
He is the greatest

Sabke bech rehke bhi akela pan sa mehsoos tha
Stress badnelaga tha
Mei thoda sa confuse tha
Par khoya nahi meine khudko
Shayat soch mei dalneki
Koshish mei hai
Rukko
Jao jhukko
Aur matha teko
Khudake saamne
Madad karenge teri woh khud aake samne
Aameen
Par jo hua hai usse meine kafi kuch seekha hai
Khush rehna seekhle
Khudse kyu roota hai
andhar se toota
Uthna majboot hoga
Zindagi mei
Aisa kabhi nai bolna ke zindagi hai meri
Gandagi mei
Jo bhi hota hai sab ke peeche kuch na kuch wajah
Dukhi tha mei 3 din
Lekin aj firse maza
aane laga hai
Abba pure theekh hogaye
Teri raza hai
Takleefo se ladke aur aage
Chala gaya mei
Kal toota tha lekin
Aj bilkul naya mei
Mei laut aya hu tere pass
Kaha tha chala gaya mei

#thankstogod #emiwaybantai #universe

snippet.title: Brandy and Monica go head-to-head in Verzuz
snippet.description:
One of the fiercest modern day diva showdowns came to a head Monday tonight (Aug. 31) as R&B legends Brandy and Monica faced off in the ultimate Verzuz battle. Hosted live at Tyler Perry Studios, the two vocal giants played their top hits for over 1 million fans ‚Äî who joined the party within just the first 30 minutes. Stars like Keke Palmer, Fantasia, Bryan Michael Cox, Missy Elliott, Johnta Austin, Solange and Jimmy Jam even tuned in to watch the celebration of over 20 years of musical mastery. 

The livestream began promptly with a DJ mix of Atlanta artists to get the crowd warmed up for the main event presented by Ciroc in partnership with Live Nation initiative Femme It Forward. Then, the real battle began... and the rest was Verzuz history.

Watch Brandy and Monica's Verzuz above! #Brandy #Monica #Verzuz

snippet.title: NVIDIA RTX 3090, 3080, 3070 Specs, Cooler, Price, & Release Date
snippet.description:
NVIDIA today officially announced its RTX 3090, RTX 3080, and RTX 3070 video cards with Ampere GPUs, including specifications, cooler design, pricing, and release dates.
Sponsor: Get 10% off Squarespace purchases (https://geni.us/BqEpf)

Grab a GamersNexus Wireframe Mouse Mat on the GN store: https://store.gamersnexus.net/products/gn-wireframe-mouse-mat
Or a GPU Tear-Down medium modmat for upcoming disassemblies! https://store.gamersnexus.net/products/medium-modmat-gpu

ARTICLE of this news item in written format: https://www.gamersnexus.net/news-pc/3615-nvidia-rtx-3090-3080-3070-specs-release-price

ROUND-UP OF CUSTOM RTX 3000 SERIES CARDS (from EVGA, ASUS, MSI, Gigabyte, & Zotac): https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7puH-8aCfBY

NVIDIA's specs are only one aspect worth discussing, but pricing is quick and easy: $500 for the RTX 3070, $700 for the RTX 3080, and $1500 for the RTX 3090. The RTX 3090 is being positioned as a Titan replacement, as evidenced in part by limited SLI accessibility indicated on the 3080 and 3070, and it's not meant to be thought of as an NVIDIA GTX 1080 Ti replacement. That said, NVIDIA is trying hard to bury its 1080 Ti and pull buyers forward to the new generation. We'll have to test them to see whether that's worth it. In the interim, partner cards will still have traditional cooler designs, but NVIDIA's reference design got creative and intends to push air straight into the CPU cooler (or rear of the case with an AIO/CLC) on one half of the card, but out the PCIe slot on the other half. We'll be discussing in this content, given our extensive thermal testing experience, what that design means for CPU tower and liquid coolers. It'll easily be the most interesting angle with these cards.

Like our content? Please consider becoming our Patron to support us: http://www.patreon.com/gamersnexus

Intel i7-10700K on Amazon: https://geni.us/Io2g98

AMD R5 3600 (non-XT) on Amazon: https://geni.us/Czsy
AMD R7 3700X on Amazon: https://geni.us/QDP6KIV

snippet.title: Police declare riot outside Mayor Ted Wheeler's apartment building
snippet.description:
People started a fire and vandalized a minority-owned dental office. Police deployed crowd control munitions and made 19 arrests.

On Monday night, Portland police declared a riot outside Mayor Ted Wheeler's apartment complex in Northwest Portland after protesters broke windows, burglarized a business, shot off fireworks, lit a picnic table on fire and set a fire inside an occupied apartment building. Police said they made 19 arrests.

Earlier in the evening, protesters gathered in the North Park Blocks in Northwest Portland for another night of demonstrations. A social media post said the group was calling for Mayor Ted Wheeler to resign.

The night's theme centered around an "unhappy birthday" celebration as Monday is Wheeler‚Äôs birthday.

Full story: https://www.kgw.com/article/news/local/protests/protesters-gather-in-north-park-blocks-for-unhappy-birthday-rally-for-portland-mayor/283-c63c8e81-50e0-41e1-aa3c-931f6779e3a7

Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/c/KGWNews8
Get the KGW app: https://kgw.com/appredirect

snippet.title: NVIDIA GeForce RTX 30 Series | Official Launch Event
snippet.description:
To view this in 4K resolution, please watch here: https://youtu.be/E98hC9e__Xs 

Announcing the all-new GeForce RTX 30 Series graphics cards, NVIDIA‚Äôs 2nd gen of RTX and greatest-ever generational leap. Powered by the NVIDIA Ampere Architecture, they deliver up to 2X performance over the previous generation for real-time ray tracing and AI.

Also announced: RTX is coming to Fortnite and Call of Duty: Black Ops Cold War, new features and apps including NVIDIA Reflex for low latency competitive gaming, NVIDIA Broadcast to turn any room into a home studio with AI, NVIDIA Omniverse Machinima for video game storytelling, NVIDIA RTX IO for near-instant game loading, and much more. 

For details on the GeForce RTX 30 Series and an overview of all the announcements, go to https://www.nvidia.com/en-us/geforce/news/introducing-rtx-30-series-graphics-cards

- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

snippet.title: Confinement Episode 8 TRAILER!
snippet.description:
Ayyy it's been a while, life kinda went downhill but it went uphill like 1000% now so I'm making stuff again. Hope y'all enjoy this trailer! It's mostly conceptual so the episode might actually look a bit different in the end, I've got a lot of pieces to pick up. I hope you're all being present and come to realise you're enough. 

Stunning music by @Zalinki  
Lovely voice talent by @Stealthy Zoroark & @SammyCzewski 
Follow these beautiful souls and give them immense love, also Stealthy Zoroark is looking for voice work so hit him up on Fiverr (( https://www.fiverr.com/stealthyzoroark/create-a-voice-over-with-requested-tone-and-accent ))

Follow/support ME on these things: 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Lord_Bung
https://www.instagram.com/whorungthedung/
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/user?u=5009181

Characters and locations are directly from/inspired by the SCP Foundation Wiki, please check it out for spooky stuff http://www.scp-wiki.net/ (this is a non-canonical story) This video is licensed under CC-BY-SA 3.0

snippet.title: Dead by Daylight | The Realm Beyond | Part 1
snippet.description:

snippet.title: NVIDIA GeForce RTX 30 Series | Official Launch Event
snippet.description:
To view this in 4K resolution, please watch here: https://youtu.be/E98hC9e__Xs 

Announcing the all-new GeForce RTX 30 Series graphics cards, NVIDIA‚Äôs 2nd gen of RTX and greatest-ever generational leap. Powered by the NVIDIA Ampere Architecture, they deliver up to 2X performance over the previous generation for real-time ray tracing and AI.

Also announced: RTX is coming to Fortnite and Call of Duty: Black Ops Cold War, new features and apps including NVIDIA Reflex for low latency competitive gaming, NVIDIA Broadcast to turn any room into a home studio with AI, NVIDIA Omniverse Machinima for video game storytelling, NVIDIA RTX IO for near-instant game loading, and much more. 

For details on the GeForce RTX 30 Series and an overview of all the announcements, go to https://www.nvidia.com/en-us/geforce/news/introducing-rtx-30-series-graphics-cards

Timestamps:
01:12 - Jensen Huang, CEO: Welcome and Overview
03:46 - Fortnite ray tracing and DLSS reveal
04:35 - NVIDIA Reflex reveal - improve esports reaction time
06:21 - NVIDIA Broadcast reveal and demonstration - enhanced streaming features
09:04 - NVIDIA Omniverse Machinima reveal
10:32 - Mount & Blade II: Bannerlord Machinima demo
11:29 - Advances in RTX ray tracing and DLSS
17:21 - Introducing RTX Ampere GPU
19:23 - RTX Ampere Demo: Marbles at Night
22:50 - Next Gen RTX Games and NVIDIA RTX IO reveal
24:12 - Cyberpunk 2077 RTX Trailer
25:12 - Introducing the GeForce RTX 3080 - our new flagship
27:31 - Overview of GeForce RTX 3080 technologies
30:39 - Introducing the GeForce RTX 3070
31:30 - Performance imrprovements: Pascal v Turing v Ampere
32:49 - Call of Duty: Cold War ray tracing reveal
34:12 - Introducing the GeForce RTX 3090
35:45 - Gaming Creator Reactions to 8K Gaming
37:20 - Summary and wrap - thank you for watching!

snippet.title: Jeremy Clarkson gave us a tour of his farm shop
snippet.description:
We've visited Jeremy a few times during his transition into farm life. On our latest trip to Diddly Squat, he gave us a tour of the farm shop, and we've got to say... we were pretty impressed.
Not only has he filled the shelves between our visits, he's also ventured into the world of online shopping, launching https://www.diddlysquatfarmshop.com/ where you can order seasonal products like lamb. 

Pre-order some of Jeremy's lamb: https://www.diddlysquatfarmshop.com/

snippet.title: NVIDIA RTX 3090, 3080, 3070 Specs, Cooler, Price, & Release Date
snippet.description:
NVIDIA today officially announced its RTX 3090, RTX 3080, and RTX 3070 video cards with Ampere GPUs, including specifications, cooler design, pricing, and release dates.
Sponsor: Get 10% off Squarespace purchases (https://geni.us/BqEpf)

Grab a GamersNexus Wireframe Mouse Mat on the GN store: https://store.gamersnexus.net/products/gn-wireframe-mouse-mat
Or a GPU Tear-Down medium modmat for upcoming disassemblies! https://store.gamersnexus.net/products/medium-modmat-gpu

ARTICLE of this news item in written format: https://www.gamersnexus.net/news-pc/3615-nvidia-rtx-3090-3080-3070-specs-release-price

ROUND-UP OF CUSTOM RTX 3000 SERIES CARDS (from EVGA, ASUS, MSI, Gigabyte, & Zotac): https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7puH-8aCfBY

NVIDIA's specs are only one aspect worth discussing, but pricing is quick and easy: $500 for the RTX 3070, $700 for the RTX 3080, and $1500 for the RTX 3090. The RTX 3090 is being positioned as a Titan replacement, as evidenced in part by limited SLI accessibility indicated on the 3080 and 3070, and it's not meant to be thought of as an NVIDIA GTX 1080 Ti replacement. That said, NVIDIA is trying hard to bury its 1080 Ti and pull buyers forward to the new generation. We'll have to test them to see whether that's worth it. In the interim, partner cards will still have traditional cooler designs, but NVIDIA's reference design got creative and intends to push air straight into the CPU cooler (or rear of the case with an AIO/CLC) on one half of the card, but out the PCIe slot on the other half. We'll be discussing in this content, given our extensive thermal testing experience, what that design means for CPU tower and liquid coolers. It'll easily be the most interesting angle with these cards.

Like our content? Please consider becoming our Patron to support us: http://www.patreon.com/gamersnexus

Intel i7-10700K on Amazon: https://geni.us/Io2g98
Intel i9-10900K on Amazon: https://geni.us/Tps89G0
AMD R3 3300X on Amazon: https://geni.us/rP3j
AMD R9 3900X on Amazon: https://geni.us/31e4Wc
AMD R5 3600 (non-XT) on Amazon: https://geni.us/Czsy
AMD R7 3700X on Amazon: https://geni.us/QDP6KIV

One of the fiercest modern day diva showdowns came to a head Monday tonight (Aug. 31) as R&B legends Brandy and Monica faced off in the ultimate Verzuz battle. Hosted live at Tyler Perry Studios, the two vocal giants played their top hits for over 1 million fans ‚Äî who joined the party within just the first 30 minutes. Stars like Keke Palmer, Fantasia, Bryan Michael Cox, Missy Elliott, Johnta Austin, Solange and Jimmy Jam even tuned in to watch the celebration of over 20 years of musical mastery. 

The livestream began promptly with a DJ mix of Atlanta artists to get the crowd warmed up for the main event presented by Ciroc in partnership with Live Nation initiative Femme It Forward. Then, the real battle began... and the rest was Verzuz history.

Watch Brandy and Monica's Verzuz above! #Brandy #Monica #Verzuz

- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements

- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

snippet.title: Apple's Massive Product Launch - New 10.8" iPad Air, iPhone 12, Apple Watch Series 6, and More!

Apple is also said to be releasing two Apple Watch models an Apple Watch Series 6 and an update to the Apple Watch Series 3. Plus a new 10.8 iPad Air 4th generation, smaller and lower cost HomePod, new Apple Headphones, Apple Airtags, and the possibility of a brand new Apple TV.

snippet.title: Confinement Episode 8 TRAILER!
snippet.description:
Ayyy it's been a while, life kinda went downhill but it went uphill like 1000% now so I'm making stuff again. Hope y'all enjoy this trailer! It's mostly conceptual so the episode might actually look a bit different in the end, I've got a lot of pieces to pick up. I hope you're all being present and come to realise you're enough.

snippet.title: Sexual Harassment | Real Talk Season 2 Episode 4
snippet.description:
How would you know you‚Äôre being sexually harassed?

In this episode, the cast speak up about their unfortunate experience of being sexually harassed and give advice on what we should do if such a thing were to happen, not only to us, but to others as well.

If you have experienced any form of sexual harassment and are in need of help, please visit:

Sexual Assault Care Centre
http://sacc.aware.org.sg/

AWARE Singapore
https://www.aware.org.sg/

Subscribe for more content like this: http://bit.ly/SubscribeMOSG

snippet.title: Manpower Minister Josephine Teo getting emotional when speaking on the issue of jobs
snippet.description:
Manpower Minister Josephine Teo got emotional when she wrapped up her speech in Parliament on Tuesday (Sept 1), where she spoke on the issue of jobs. 
She said her ministry will help Singaporeans through the storm, however long it lasts.


Read more: https://tdy.sg/3bhhfY3

snippet.localized.title: Arsenal vs Liverpool | Key Moments | Community Shield 2020
snippet.localized.description:
Heads Up FA Cup Final winners Arsenal beat Premier League champions Liverpool on penalties to win the Community Shield, after Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang and Takumi Minamino scored for their teams. 

Follow @EmiratesFACup on Twitter for in-game highlights and match updates!
https://twitter.com/emiratesfacup

snippet.title: The Batman - DC FanDome Teaser
snippet.description:
Robert Pattinson is #TheBatman.

https://www.instagram.com/thebatman/
https://www.facebook.com/thebatman
https://twitter.com/thebatman
http://thebatman.com

From Warner Bros. Pictures comes ‚ÄúThe Batman,‚Äù with director Matt Reeves (the ‚ÄúPlanet of the Apes‚Äù films) at the helm and with Robert Pattinson (‚ÄúTenet,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Lighthouse,‚Äù ‚ÄúGood Time‚Äù) starring as Gotham City‚Äôs vigilante detective, Batman, and billionaire Bruce Wayne.

Also in the star-studded ensemble as Gotham‚Äôs famous and infamous cast of characters are Zo√´ Kravitz (‚ÄúFantastic Beasts: The Crimes of Grindelwald,‚Äù ‚ÄúMad Max: Fury Road‚Äù) as Selina Kyle; Paul Dano (‚ÄúLove & Mercy,‚Äù ‚Äú12 Years a Slave‚Äù) as Edward Nashton; Jeffrey Wright (the ‚ÄúHunger Games‚Äù films) as the GCPD‚Äôs James Gordon; John Turturro (the ‚ÄúTransformers‚Äù films) as Carmine Falcone; Peter Sarsgaard (‚ÄúThe Magnificent Seven,‚Äù ‚ÄúBlack Mass‚Äù) as Gotham D.A. Gil Colson; Barry Keoghan (‚ÄúDunkirk‚Äù) as Officer Stanley Merkel; Jayme Lawson (‚ÄúFarewell Amor‚Äù) as mayoral candidate Bella Re√°l; with Andy Serkis (the ‚ÄúPlanet of the Apes‚Äù films, ‚ÄúBlack Panther‚Äù) as Alfred; and Colin Farrell (‚ÄúFantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them,‚Äù ‚ÄúDumbo‚Äù) as Oswald Cobblepot.

‚ÄúThe Batman‚Äù was written by Matt Reeves & Peter Craig.  Reeves and Dylan Clark (the ‚ÄúPlanet of the Apes‚Äù films) are producing the film, with Simon Emanuel, Michael E. Uslan, Walter Hamada and Chantal Nong Vo serving as executive producers.  Reeves‚Äô behind-the-scenes creative team includes Oscar-nominated director of photography Greig Fraser (‚ÄúLion,‚Äù upcoming ‚ÄúDune‚Äù); his ‚ÄúPlanet of the Apes‚Äù production designer, James Chinlund; editors William Hoy (the ‚ÄúPlanet of the Apes‚Äù films) and Tyler Nelson (‚ÄúRememory‚Äù); Oscar-winning VFX supervisor Dan Lemmon (‚ÄúThe Jungle Book‚Äù); Oscar-nominated SFX supervisor Dominic Tuohy (‚Äú1917,‚Äù ‚ÄúStar Wars: Episode IX ‚Äì The Rise of Skywalker‚Äù); Oscar-nominated sound mixer Stuart Wilson (‚Äú1917,‚Äù the ‚ÄúStar Wars‚Äù franchise); Oscar-winning costume designer Jacqueline Durran (‚Äú1917,‚Äù ‚ÄúLittle Women,‚Äù ‚ÄúAnna Karenina‚Äù) and costume designers Glyn Dillon (the ‚ÄúStar Wars‚Äù franchise) and David Crossman (‚Äú1917,‚Äù the ‚ÄúStar Wars‚Äù franchise); hair designer Zoe Tahir (upcoming ‚ÄúNo Time to Die,‚Äù ‚ÄúSpectre‚Äù); and Oscar-nominated makeup designer Naomi Donne (‚Äú1917‚Äù).

Based on characters from DC.  Batman was created by Bob Kane with Bill Finger.  ‚ÄúThe Batman‚Äù is set to open in theaters October 1, 2021 in select 3D and 2D and IMAX theaters and will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures.

snippet.title: Wonder Woman 1984 - Official Main Trailer
snippet.description:
The new era of Wonder Woman begins here. #WW84 only in theaters.
 
http://www.facebook.com/WonderWomanFilm
http://twitter.com/WonderWomanFilm
http://www.instagram.com/wonderwomanfilm
http://wonderwoman1984.com
 
Fast forward to the 1980s as Wonder Woman‚Äôs next big screen adventure finds her facing two all-new foes: Max Lord and The Cheetah.  
 
With director Patty Jenkins back at the helm and Gal Gadot returning in the title role, ‚ÄúWonder Woman 1984‚Äù is Warner Bros. Pictures‚Äô follow up to the DC Super Hero‚Äôs first outing, 2017‚Äôs record-breaking ‚ÄúWonder Woman,‚Äù which took in $822 million at the worldwide box office.  The film also stars Chris Pine as Steve Trevor, Kristen Wiig as The Cheetah, Pedro Pascal as Max Lord, Robin Wright as Antiope, and Connie Nielsen as Hippolyta.
 
Charles Roven, Deborah Snyder, Zack Snyder, Patty Jenkins, Gal Gadot and Stephen Jones are producing the film.  Rebecca Steel Roven Oakley, Richard Suckle, Marianne Jenkins, Geoff Johns, Walter Hamada, Chantal Nong Vo and Wesley Coller are the executive producers.
 
Patty Jenkins directed from a screenplay she wrote with Geoff Johns & David Callaham, story by Jenkins & Johns, based on characters from DC.  Joining the director behind the scenes are several members of her ‚ÄúWonder Woman‚Äù team, including director of photography Matthew Jensen, Oscar-nominated production designer Aline Bonetto (‚ÄúAm√©lie‚Äù), and Oscar-winning costume designer Lindy Hemming (‚ÄúTopsy-Turvy‚Äù).  Oscar-nominated editor Richard Pearson (‚ÄúUnited 93‚Äù) is cutting the film.  The music is by Oscar-winning composer Hans Zimmer (‚ÄúDunkirk,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Lion King‚Äù).
 
Warner Bros. Pictures Presents an Atlas Entertainment/Stone Quarry Production, a Patty Jenkins Film, ‚ÄúWonder Woman 1984.‚Äù  Set to open in theaters in 2D and 3D in select theaters and IMAX, it will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures.
 
This film is rated PG-13 for sequences of action and violence.

snippet.localized.title: Wonder Woman 1984 - Official Main Trailer
snippet.localized.description:
The new era of Wonder Woman begins here. #WW84 only in theaters.
 
http://www.facebook.com/WonderWomanFilm
http://twitter.com/WonderWomanFilm
http://www.instagram.com/wonderwomanfilm
http://wonderwoman1984.com
 
Fast forward to the 1980s as Wonder Woman‚Äôs next big screen adventure finds her facing two all-new foes: Max Lord and The Cheetah.  
 
With director Patty Jenkins back at the helm and Gal Gadot returning in the title role, ‚ÄúWonder Woman 1984‚Äù is Warner Bros. Pictures‚Äô follow up to the DC Super Hero‚Äôs first outing, 2017‚Äôs record-breaking ‚ÄúWonder Woman,‚Äù which took in $822 million at the worldwide box office.  The film also stars Chris Pine as Steve Trevor, Kristen Wiig as The Cheetah, Pedro Pascal as Max Lord, Robin Wright as Antiope, and Connie Nielsen as Hippolyta.
 
Charles Roven, Deborah Snyder, Zack Snyder, Patty Jenkins, Gal Gadot and Stephen Jones are producing the film.  Rebecca Steel Roven Oakley, Richard Suckle, Marianne Jenkins, Geoff Johns, Walter Hamada, Chantal Nong Vo and Wesley Coller are the executive producers.
 
Patty Jenkins directed from a screenplay she wrote with Geoff Johns & David Callaham, story by Jenkins & Johns, based on characters from DC.  Joining the director behind the scenes are several members of her ‚ÄúWonder Woman‚Äù team, including director of photography Matthew Jensen, Oscar-nominated production designer Aline Bonetto (‚ÄúAm√©lie‚Äù), and Oscar-winning costume designer Lindy Hemming (‚ÄúTopsy-Turvy‚Äù).  Oscar-nominated editor Richard Pearson (‚ÄúUnited 93‚Äù) is cutting the film.  The music is by Oscar-winning composer Hans Zimmer (‚ÄúDunkirk,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Lion King‚Äù).
 
Warner Bros. Pictures Presents an Atlas Entertainment/Stone Quarry Production, a Patty Jenkins Film, ‚ÄúWonder Woman 1984.‚Äù  Set to open in theaters in 2D and 3D in select theaters and IMAX, it will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures.
 
This film is rated PG-13 for sequences of action and violence.

ùô≤ùöäùöïùöï ùöòùöè ùô≥ùöûùöùùö¢: ùô±ùöïùöäùöåùöî ùôæùöôùöú ùô≤ùöòùöïùöç ùöÜùöäùöõ ùö†ùöíùöïùöï ùöçùöõùöòùöô ùöôùöïùöäùö¢ùöéùöõùöú ùöíùöóùöùùöò ùöùùöëùöé ùöçùöéùöôùöùùöëùöú ùöòùöè ùöùùöëùöé ùô≤ùöòùöïùöç ùöÜùöäùöõ‚Äôùöú ùöüùöòùöïùöäùöùùöíùöïùöé ùöêùöéùöòùöôùöòùöïùöíùöùùöíùöåùöäùöï ùöãùöäùöùùöùùöïùöé ùöòùöè ùöùùöëùöé ùöéùöäùöõùöïùö¢ ùü∑ùüøùüæùü∂ùöú. ùô∏ùöó ùöä ùöêùöõùöíùöôùöôùöíùöóùöê ùöúùöíùöóùöêùöïùöé-ùöôùöïùöäùö¢ùöéùöõ ùô≤ùöäùöñùöôùöäùöíùöêùöó, ùöôùöïùöäùö¢ùöéùöõùöú ùö†ùöíùöïùöï ùöçùöéùöúùöåùöéùöóùöç ùöíùöóùöùùöò ùöùùöëùöé ùöçùöäùöõùöî ùöåùöéùöóùöùùöéùöõ ùöòùöè ùöä ùöêùöïùöòùöãùöäùöï ùöåùöòùöóùöúùöôùöíùöõùöäùöåùö¢ ùöäùöïùöòùöóùöêùöúùöíùöçùöé ùöíùöåùöòùöóùöíùöå ùöåùöëùöäùöõùöäùöåùöùùöéùöõùöú ùöÜùöòùöòùöçùöú, ùôºùöäùöúùöòùöó, ùöäùöóùöç ùô∑ùöûùöçùöúùöòùöó, ùöäùöú ùö†ùöéùöïùöï ùöäùöú ùöä ùöóùöéùö† ùöåùöäùöúùöù ùöòùöè ùöòùöôùöéùöõùöäùöùùöíùöüùöéùöú ùöùùöò ùöúùöùùöòùöô ùöä ùöôùöïùöòùöù ùöçùöéùöåùöäùöçùöéùöú ùöíùöó ùöùùöëùöé ùöñùöäùöîùöíùöóùöê.

snippet.title: Wonder Woman 1984 - Official Main Trailer
snippet.description:
The new era of Wonder Woman begins here. #WW84 only in theaters.
 
http://www.facebook.com/WonderWomanFilm
http://twitter.com/WonderWomanFilm
http://www.instagram.com/wonderwomanfilm
http://wonderwoman1984.com
 
Fast forward to the 1980s as Wonder Woman‚Äôs next big screen adventure finds her facing two all-new foes: Max Lord and The Cheetah.  
 
With director Patty Jenkins back at the helm and Gal Gadot returning in the title role, ‚ÄúWonder Woman 1984‚Äù is Warner Bros. Pictures‚Äô follow up to the DC Super Hero‚Äôs first outing, 2017‚Äôs record-breaking ‚ÄúWonder Woman,‚Äù which took in $822 million at the worldwide box office.  The film also stars Chris Pine as Steve Trevor, Kristen Wiig as The Cheetah, Pedro Pascal as Max Lord, Robin Wright as Antiope, and Connie Nielsen as Hippolyta.
 
Charles Roven, Deborah Snyder, Zack Snyder, Patty Jenkins, Gal Gadot and Stephen Jones are producing the film.  Rebecca Steel Roven Oakley, Richard Suckle, Marianne Jenkins, Geoff Johns, Walter Hamada, Chantal Nong Vo and Wesley Coller are the executive producers.
 
Patty Jenkins directed from a screenplay she wrote with Geoff Johns & David Callaham, story by Jenkins & Johns, based on characters from DC.  Joining the director behind the scenes are several members of her ‚ÄúWonder Woman‚Äù team, including director of photography Matthew Jensen, Oscar-nominated production designer Aline Bonetto (‚ÄúAm√©lie‚Äù), and Oscar-winning costume designer Lindy Hemming (‚ÄúTopsy-Turvy‚Äù).  Oscar-nominated editor Richard Pearson (‚ÄúUnited 93‚Äù) is cutting the film.  The music is by Oscar-winning composer Hans Zimmer (‚ÄúDunkirk,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Lion King‚Äù).
 
Warner Bros. Pictures Presents an Atlas Entertainment/Stone Quarry Production, a Patty Jenkins Film, ‚ÄúWonder Woman 1984.‚Äù  Set to open in theaters in 2D and 3D in select theaters and IMAX, it will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures.
 
This film is rated PG-13 for sequences of action and violence.

snippet.title: Oklahoma City Thunder vs Houston Rockets | August 31, 2020
snippet.description: Led by Chris Paul‚Äôs 28 points (15 in the 4th quarter), 7 rebounds and 3 assists, the Thunder defeated the Rockets, 104-100, in Game 6. Additionally for the Thunder, Danilo Gallinari added 25 points and 5 rebounds in the victory, while James Harden tallied 32 points, 8 rebounds and 7 assists for the Rockets in the losing effort. This best-of-seven series is now tied, 3-3. Game 7 will take place on Wednesday, September 2 at 9:00 p.m. ET

snippet.title: Coronavirus-Update #54: Eine Empfehlung f√ºr den Herbst | NDR Podcast
snippet.description:
Christian Drosten ist zur√ºck mit einer XXL-Folge. Es geht um Masken und Aerosole, Immunit√§t, Virusst√§mme und eine neue Teststrategie.

Die Manuskripte aller Folgen:
https://www.ndr.de/nachrichten/info/podcastcoronavirus102.html

Alle Fragen und Antworten zu Corona auf unserer FAQ-Seite: https://www.ndr.de/ratgeber/gesundheit/corona100.html 

Kein Tag vergeht ohne neue Nachrichten zum Coronavirus Sars-CoV-2. L√§ngst haben wir uns an Ma√ünahmen wie Mundschutz, Abstand und Hygieneregeln gew√∂hnt. Und noch immer ist kein Ende der Pandemie in Sicht. In unserem w√∂chentlichen Podcast wollen wir verl√§sslich √ºber neue Erkenntnisse der Forschung informieren. Wie steht es um einen Impfstoff? Wie entwickelt sich die Test-Strategie? Besteht Hoffnung auf ein Medikament? Die NDR Wissenschaftsredakteurin Korinna Hennig spricht dazu im Wechsel mit Christian Drosten, Leiter der Virologie in der Berliner Charit√©, und mit Sandra Ciesek, Leiterin des Instituts f√ºr Medizinische Virologie am Universit√§tsklinikum Frankfurt. Dabei soll es nicht um Panikmache gehen - sondern ganz im Gegenteil: Der Podcast "Coronavirus-Update" will informieren, einordnen und Hintergr√ºnde liefern.

Die Manuskripte aller Folgen:
https://www.ndr.de/nachrichten/info/podcastcoronavirus102.html

Alle Fragen und Antworten zu Corona auf unserer FAQ-Seite: https://www.ndr.de/ratgeber/gesundheit/corona100.html 

Wer eine Frage f√ºr die Podcast-Interviews mit Christian Drosten und Sandra Ciesek hat, kann diese gerne per Mail schicken an: meinefrage@ndr.de

snippet.title: TENET beweist, dass Christopher Nolan √ºberbewertet ist
snippet.description:
#TENET ist das neue Kino-Meisterwerk von Regie-Meister Christopher Nolan! Oder doch nicht? Meine Kritik und Review, die an diesem Legenden-Status etwas auszusetzen hat...

Obwohl ich noch nicht einmal "The Dark Knight" f√ºr einen wirklichen "perfekten" Film halte, gibt es aber einen einzigen (!), wirklich perfekten Film von Nolan - aber dar√ºber rede ich im noch ausf√ºhrlicheren Spoiler-Podcast: https://open.spotify.com/episode/2wR6u88ogE1Xn4ZRgKnBTR?si=qgT0BEJgQzyWyG9RtD0yIQ

Meine Wertung zum Film findet ihr wie immer auf Letterboxd: https://letterboxd.com/Nerdkultur/

------------------------------------------------------

TENET l√§uft trotz Corona seit dem 26. August in Deutschland nur im Kino. Regie f√ºhrt nat√ºrlich #ChristopherNolan (Inception, Memento), der wieder ohne seinen Bruder Jonathan Nolan (Westworld, The Dark Knight, The Prestige) auskommt. Die Kamera f√ºhrt zum dritten Mal f√ºr ihn Hoyte Van Hoytema (Dunkirk, Interstellar) und der Schnitt ist erstmals von Jennifer Lame (Marriage Story, Hereditary). Statt Hans Zimmer (wegen Dune 2020) kommt die Musik von Ludwig G√∂ransson (Creed, Black Pnather, The Mandalorian).

Wie f√ºr Nolan mittlerweile √ºblich hat auch Michael Caine (Batman Begins) eine kleine Rolle. Die absoluten Hauptrollen gehen an John David Washington (BlacKkKlansman), Robert Pattinson (The Batman, Twilight, The Lighthouse) und Kenneth Branagh (Mord im Orient-Express). Auch neu dabei sind Elizabeth Debicki (Widows, Guardians of the Galaxy Vol. 2), Aaron Taylor-Johnson (Kick-Ass, Avengers: Age of Ultron) und Cl√©mence Po√©sy (Harry Potter).

snippet.title: Die Abschleppbr√ºder vom Autobahnkreuz | die nordreportage | NDR Doku
snippet.description:
Die Br√ºder Oliver und Rouven Fl√∂rke sind Abschleppunternehmer, 24 Stunden erreichbar und am Lehrter Kreuz zwischen der A2 und A7 unterwegs, zwei der meistbefahrenen Autobahnen in Deutschland. Die beiden leiten seit einem Jahr gemeinsam das Familienunternehmen mit 20 Mitarbeitenden. Doch der Seniorchef, ihr Vater, kann sich immer noch nicht so ganz trennen.

Mit Sorge betrachten die Br√ºder die Entwicklung auf den Autobahnen. Ihr Eindruck: Trotz aller Pr√§vention und vermehrter Kontrollen, gibt es immer mehr Autobahnunf√§lle mit schweren Personensch√§den. Autobahneins√§tze sind auch f√ºr die Abschlepper gef√§hrlich, denn sie arbeiten dann oft im flie√üenden Verkehr.

"Die Nordreportage" begleitet das Br√ºderpaar w√§hrend des Ferienverkehrs in ihrem ersten gemeinsamen Jahr als Leiter des Unternehmens.
